   <header>
    <h1>
     Hot-rodding the Fuel Injection
    </h1>
    <p>
     Posted by Mike West to the VintagVW list
    </p>
   </header>
   <div class="nav">
    <a href="/~keen/west/darkness.html">
     ‚Üê Back to Pushing Back the Darkness
    </a>
   </div>
   <dl class="meta">
